<br>
If you have a chanter, then I would say heal the tank and let the chanter do his/her job.  You can probably keep the mobs off the cleric or do back up heals on the cleric long enough to get all the mobs mezzed.  <br>
<br>
If you don't have a chanter or the ability to at least root park the mobs, then a cleric heal would just land all those mobs on the cleric, which would probably cause the entire group to die anyway.<br>
<br>
